{"tid":1917061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣研成15分鐘武肺快速試劑 , 台灣強調： 與中國無關","createTime":"2020-03-09T09:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T10:00:58.000Z","uid":25468,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1c346c7ad2d075b7d4d960fadbe41b618cebfe0d","tid":1917061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-20200309122000_1fe0_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-20200309122000_1fe0_large.jpg&h=e160cccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣中央研究院周日宣布，已經成功合成能辨識武漢肺炎病毒蛋白質的單株抗體群，將與廠商談合作生產，未來可在15至20分鐘內完成病毒測試。中央社則報道，中國大陸方面傳出研究是來自中方成果，台灣中研院院長廖俊智周一表示，這完全是中研院成果，與中國無關。<br />\n<br />\n目前檢測武漢肺炎病毒是以核酸檢驗方式進行，平均約4小時，且需特殊儀器。台灣中研院成功合成能辨識武漢肺炎病毒蛋白質的單株抗體群，可作為檢測快篩裝置的關鍵試劑。廖俊智表示，此次成果是中研院各團隊2月初已開始通力合作，快速合成病毒核蛋白抗原。其中，楊安綏團隊運用數十年來累積的技術，日以繼夜進行抗體合成及篩選，才有此項重要成就。<br />\n<br />\n廖俊智強調，防疫是與時間賽跑，除了院內各研究團隊共同合作，中研院並建立台灣學研單位合作平台，今次成果將與平台共享，加速研發武漢肺炎快速篩檢工具、藥物與疫苗，合作抗疫。他說，楊安綏實驗室10多年來深耕基礎研究，重視醫學具體成果，團隊去年也曾針對非洲豬瘟研發免疫抗原檢測裝置，此次比預期快2個月達成目標，相當令人振奮。<br />\n<br />\n研究團隊將在經濟部安排下，與多家廠商研究生產快篩檢測的原型產品。一切順利的話，希望能在3到4個月內通過衛福部驗證及進入量產，加快病人檢體的驗證，以作大規模臨床應用。<br />\n<br />\n對於台灣中研院合成能辨識武漢肺炎病毒蛋白質單株抗體群，台灣傳媒報道，中國大陸有媒體表示台灣中研院的試劑是取自中國大陸，台灣中研院長廖俊智周一說，完全是中研院成果，「與中國一點關係都沒有」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27678/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2-%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91-27684/%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F27678%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%258A%2591-27684%2F%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%258A%2591&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=1d365e19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27678/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2-%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91-27684/%E8%A9%A6%E5%8A%91</a>"},{"pid":"4bab196106332e21af712df55971f4713f87876f","tid":1917061,"uid":1724,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZQWidH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZQWidH.jpg&h=fc3137ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a06a426aa13677bcd25a0e09dc955eaccb4be0e","tid":1917061,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f496595ec8bf415e3148ab13485e60241a62ba","tid":1917061,"uid":137506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b682ba2f183d271ee95c2b5501c118916dfa4df","tid":1917061,"uid":263534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"有彩攞又爭住狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7deed9d2883c03a1a150058a0e49d7ffb7231015","tid":1917061,"uid":202426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"與中國一點關係都沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d552a4